Package: ingov
Title: Indiana / Bloomington Open Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for Indiana / Bloomington Socrata Open Data portal.
    Provides discovery, search, and data access for police, fire, government,
    transportation, utilities, and other city datasets.
